(4121, 700, 'I wanna see.', '* sneaks off to watch Aquarius in his inventing process.', 9, '+1 Evade, +1 creativity, +1 intelligence'),
(4122, 701, 'Oh no.', '* consoles the young creatures when their treehouse falls.', 6, '+1 charisma'),
